---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { name: 'Training', href: '/dog-training' },
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Dog Training | Evolutionary K9 — Mineral Bluff, GA"
  description="Behavior training that combines classical and operant conditioning with a focus on understanding how a dog thinks and makes decisions. Training currently on pause — check back for updates."
  ogImage="/images/training.jpg"
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <div class="service-hero">
    <img src="/images/training.jpg" alt="Mastiff puppy with glasses resting on old books beside an hourglass and chalkboard" width="1900" height="1267" />
  </div>
  <section class="service-hero-title">
    <h1>Dog Training</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <div class="status-pause">
        <h3>Training is currently on "Paws"</h3>
        <p>We are not accepting any new training / consultation requests at this time. Check back here for future updates.</p>
      </div>

      <p>At Evolutionary K9, it's all about understanding your dog's behavior. We will set you on the path of critical thinking and explain how a dog's evolution has affected his biology — and through that knowledge we can learn to modify, change or adjust unwanted behaviors while at the same time earning trust and confidence and reinforcing wanted behavior.</p>

      <p>We believe one training method isn't for all dogs, so we focus on a combination of classical and operant conditioning as the foundation of training — but primary importance is the understanding of how a dog thinks and makes decisions. Our training classes are for all members of the family over the age of 14. We do offer a separate class for younger students focusing on the relationship between kids and dogs, emphasizing appropriateness as well as understanding how dogs view the young.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
